name: New Year's Resolution: Volunteer More
description:
This limited edition New Year's Resolution series was made just for the HEN community event ROCKING NEW YEAR JACKPOT hosted by @rblbab @Erythric @brainksy @TerosEso @ninacrypto2.  I am so excited to see who wins the jackpot!

HOWEVER, I have reached my limit of 10 items per artist, but due to a compulsion to do 12 in all my series...or multiples of 12... I have two extra NFTs.  I will do this one as a nearly free giveaway and the other as a 1/1.  Hope you enjoy the series!
